BaihongQi CMPUT301_Assignment1

This is an app which is a easy-to-use reaction timer and gameshow buzzer. Gameshow buzzers are used on shows like Jeopardy to determine who gets to answer a question by who pressed the buzzer button first. Reaction timers are used to train for such shows so that you can press the buzzer button fast to answer the question.

In the single user mode:
The game waits between 10ms and 2000ms before prompts the user to click, and the latency is recored.
In the mutiplayer mode:
 The system will record who pressed the button first and the number of players.

This app supports:

recording reaction time statistics
recording buzzer press/buzzes statistics
measuring reaction times
measuring buzzer buzzs
clearing stastistics
emailing statistics

